item.title: Barbie & The Two Abusive Parents | Domestic Violence & Narcissist Abuse
item.description: In this episode of Narcissist Apocalypse, Brandon interviews Barbie about growing up with two abusive parents. Barbie describes the emotional and physical trauma inflicted by her parents, their manipulative gaslighting, and their lack of empathy.
